    <h1>Kernel Methods & SVMs</h1>
    <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm mb-6">Machine Learning · Ch.5 of 12</p>

    <div class="bg-zinc-800 rounded-lg p-5 mb-8 callout">
      <p class="text-lg" style="max-width:none">Map data to a higher-dimensional space where it becomes linearly separable. The <strong>kernel trick</strong> computes the inner product in that space without ever visiting it. The <strong>SVM</strong> maximizes the margin between classes.</p>
    </div>

